---
import MarketingLayout from "@/layouts/MarketingLayout.astro";
import PageHeader from "../components/PageHeader.astro";
import Prose from "../components/Prose.astro";
---

<MarketingLayout
  title="About BetsPlug — sports intelligence with a public track record"
  description="We build AI football predictions and publish every result. No black boxes, no edited highlight reel — just a model with its homework on display."
  canonicalPath="/about-us"
>
    <PageHeader
      kicker="About BetsPlug"
      title="Sports intelligence, with the <span class='gradient-text-green'>homework on display</span>."
      subtitle="One AI engine. One daily Pick of the Day. Every prediction logged before kickoff and graded afterwards. Educational simulation only — 18+, no financial advice."
    />

    <Prose>
      <h2>Why we exist</h2>
      <p>
        Most "tipster" platforms hide their results — they show you yesterday's
        winners and quietly drop the losers from the slate. BetsPlug is built
        the other way around. Every prediction the engine makes is timestamped
        before kickoff, stored in a public database, and graded once the
        match ends. The number you see on our pricing page is the number our
        own server saw.
      </p>

      <h2>How it works</h2>
      <p>
        Our v8.1 engine combines XGBoost with a calibrated logistic model
        across <strong>30+ football competitions worldwide</strong>. It
        ingests Elo ratings, recent form, head-to-head history, league
        standings, and betting-market odds. For every fixture it outputs a
        win/draw/loss probability and a single confidence score.
      </p>
      <p>
        Picks are then bucketed into four tiers (Free, Silver, Gold,
        Platinum) based on the league quality and how confident the engine
        is. Higher tier = stricter filter = fewer picks per day, but a
        higher historical hit rate.
      </p>

      <h2>What we don't do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          We don't take bets, hold deposits, or process wagers. We are not a
          bookmaker.
        </li>
        <li>
          We don't give financial or betting advice. Our forecasts are
          probabilistic estimates published for educational and research
          purposes only.
        </li>
        <li>We don't promise that you'll make money. Past model performance
          is not indicative of future results.</li>
        <li>We don't hide the misses. Every graded prediction lives on the
          public track record, including the ones the engine got wrong.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Who runs this</h2>
      <p>
        BetsPlug is built and operated by a small Dutch team that ships
        every week. We're independently funded — no investor pressure to
        chase a tipster narrative. Every commit is on GitHub; our model
        artefacts live in the same repo as our pricing page.
      </p>

      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <p>
        Question, partnership, press? Drop us a note at <a
          href="mailto:hello@betsplug.com">hello@betsplug.com</a> or via the{" "}
        <a href="/contact">contact page</a>. We answer everything within
        two working days.
      </p>
    </Prose>
</MarketingLayout>
